Name: Ji'nara
Description:
First Ascendant of the Tal'darim. Ji'nara choosing this path has been corrupted by the Dark God and The Heretics. She will harvest and devour the blood and soul of all life in front of her.

Can attack ground and air units.

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target area or follow the target unit. Moving units will not engage enemies.
Root.Name: Move

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to cancel all orders and stop moving.
Root.Name: Stop

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to stay where they are and attack enemies that are within range. Units will neither chase down enemies nor move to engage.
Root.Name: Hold Position

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to move to the target point, fighting nearby enemies along the way. Targeting a unit with the Attack command orders that it be attacked until it is destroyed.
Root.Name: Attack

Root.Tooltip: Orders selected units to patrol between their current position and the target area. Units will attack enemies and move to engage nearby enemies.
Root.Name: Patrol

Root.Tooltip: The Death Fleet descends to aid the high lord Ji'nara.
Root.Name: Shadow of Death: Renaissance

Root.Tooltip:
Command Destroyers fleets to crash into the target area. After the Destroyer crashes, it will glide a certain distance, causing 60 damage (100vs Armored) to ground units passing by.

This skill can be used for three times, and the skill effect will change after each cast. Next time, it will be changed to Shadow of Death: Doom Engine.
Root.Name: Shadow of Death: Destroyer

Root.Tooltip:
Command Doom Engine fleets to crash into the target area. After the Doom Engine, it will glide a certain distance, causing 300damage (500vs Armored) to ground units passing by. The wreckage will also burn at the point of impact, causing 48 damage (vs.80vs Armored) to nearby enemy ground units every second for 5 seconds.

This skill can be used for three times, and the skill effect will change after each cast. Next time, it will be changed to Shadow of Death: Crimson Space.
Root.Name: Shadow of Death: Doom Engine

Root.Tooltip:
Command Crimson Space to crash into the target area. It will last for 16 seconds. The moment the Crimson Space debris appears, it will cause 600 damage (1000vs. Structure) to the enemy unit. When it is destroyed, it will cause 300 damage(500vs. Structure) to the enemy unit.

This skill can be used for three times, and the skill effect will change after each cast. Death Fleet is perished.
Root.Name: Shadow of Death: Crimson Space

Root.Tooltip: The Death Fleet is destroyed and can no longer be used.
Root.Name: Shadow of Death: Perished

Root.Tooltip:
Ji'nara intercepts target enemy unit and strikes it for 200 damage.

The type of damage is "Annihilation ". If this skill kills the target, Ji'nara permanently gains bonus damage.
Root.Name: Deadly Charge

Root.Tooltip:
Ji'nara Slashes an area with her scythe, stunning the enemy for 2 seconds and the heroic unit will be slowed down. Enemy units located in the outer circle take 60 damage, and this part of the damage will be converted into shields for Jinara.

In addition, when Absolute Dominance is effective, Ji'nara deals area damage and has the Annihilation effect. **Annihilation**: This skill can detonate the Seed of Annihilation. Killing the enemy will permanently provide Jinara with damage bonus.
Root.Name: Movement of Annihilation

Root.Tooltip: Ji'nara's next attack can deal area damage. When Absolute Dominance is active, this skill will be replaced by Movement of Annihilation. **Annihilation**: This skill can detonate the Seed of Annihilation. If this skill kills the target, Ji'nara permanently gains bonus damage.
Root.Name: Annihilation Overture

Root.Tooltip: Unleashes a massive wave of force in a straight line, dealing 50 damage to enemies in its path and knocking them back.
Root.Name: Destruction Wave

Root.Tooltip:
Deplete the Corruption to use Absolute Dominance. The more Corruption has, the longer the duration and cooling time Absolute Dominance has. Lasts 10.0 seconds.

Every allied unit around Jinara will increase her attack damage and skill damage, and grant her detection and map Boss attributes.

Ascendants and Martyrs provide an additional 100% increase, and Abyssal avatars provide an additional 200% increase.
Root.Name: Absolute Dominance

Root.Tooltip:
Unit born from Dark Ritual. Can apply "Seed of Annihilation" and "Seed of Chaos" to the target when casting skills and attacks.

Ji'nara's damage will detonate the seeds of chaos on the target, dealing 15 damage per stack.

Some Ji'nara's skills have an additional "Annihilation" effect. These skills can detonate the Seed of Annihilation, causing 150 damage to the target per stack, and nearby target and target with the same stack to take 150 damage.
Root.Name: Annihilation and Chaos

Root.Tooltip:
Ji'nara's normal attacks and the damage caused by detonating the seeds of annihilation also have the effect of "annihilation".

Units killed by Jinara's annihilation effect will provide a permanent damage increase to Jinara based on 50% of their supply, and provide 1 Corruption.

The current damage increase provided by the "Annihilation" effect is: 0.
Root.Name: Coup de Grace

Root.Tooltip:
Ji'nara heals 20 life and restores 20 shields each supply when a nearby enemy unit is slain. Ji'nara steals life from nearby units you control to heal herself when she is below 50 health.

Nearby Supplicant or Abyssal avatar sacrificed will reduce the cooldown of Ji'nara's skills.
Root.Name: Soul Absorption

Root.Tooltip: Allows Ji'nara's attacks to stun enemy units for 2 seconds. Heroic units are slowed.
Root.Name: Curse of Abyss

Root.Tooltip: Sends constructed units to the designated point. Workers rallied to resources will begin gathering automatically.
Root.Name: Set Rally Point

Behaviors.Tooltip: Ji'nara now has an additional 0 attack damage and 0% skill damage.
Behaviors.Name: Absolute Dominance
